name: Coupled
overview: Coupled follows 12 single, smart and young professional women looking for love who will meet face-to-face with eligible single men against the beautiful backdrop of the Caribbean islands.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: A dozen single Women wait anxiously in the Caribbean as a man a day arrives via helicopter - each man chooses which woman he would like to be "coupled " with, until they are all paired up and the fun begins.

episodes.name: Chemistry 101
episodes.overview: Coupled follows 12 single, smart and young professional women looking for love who will meet face-to-face with eligible single men against the beautiful backdrop of the Caribbean islands.

episodes.name: Instant Connection
episodes.overview: The second man to arrive has to decide which ladies he wants to keep seeing; the first couple test their chemistry in the couples' villas; the remaining ladies wait to meet the third man.

episodes.name: Chemical Attraction
episodes.overview: A text message threatens to come between one of the couples; a helicopter arrives bearing a single man.

episodes.name: At First Sight
episodes.overview: The next helicopter arrives with two guys and tensions run high for a couple that realize their political views are extremely different.

episodes.name: Love Bites
episodes.overview: A surprising rejection creates chaos among the ladies; a woman eyes someone else's man; and one of the ladies reveals an emotional part of her past.

episodes.name: Chain Reactions
episodes.overview: The latest guy to arrive at the Bungalows receives a very warm welcome leading to increased competition amongst the women. Meanwhile, the newest couple at the Villas learns that good chemistry doesn't always mean good compatibility and one of the girls tries to determine how invested her guy really is.

episodes.name: Chemistry Project
episodes.overview: When the latest guy chooses two very different women to take to the Villas, the women try to pull out all the stops in an attempt to win him over. Meanwhile, a game of truth or dare causes one relationship to be tested.

episodes.name: Mutual Distraction
episodes.overview: A surprise awaits the women in one of the final arrivals. Also: one woman leaves the island following a major partner swap.

episodes.name: Laws of Attraction
episodes.overview: The couples find out they will all be going on individual dates to test their compatibility with each other. Tensions rise as one girl puts her guy on the spot with an important question, a couple has issues when things get intimate and another couple experience their biggest fight yet.

episodes.overview: The contestants are visited by their families, who help them decide whether their island romances can survive the real world.
